{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Introduce regular drug testing for MPs and ban alcohol in Parliament",
        "additional_details": "Introduce regular drug testing for Members of Parliament to maintain integrity and trust in our legislative process.\r\n \r\nEnforce a complete ban on alcohol consumption in the UK Parliament to ensure clear-headed decision-making and uphold parliamentary dignity. This should include closing all bars within parliamentary premises to promote professionalism and accountability.\r\n \r\nWe believe these measures will strengthen the UK Parliament's integrity and commitment to ethical conduct. We request prompt consideration and implementation.\r\n",
        "background": "1. Drug Testing for all MPs: Implement regular drug testing to maintain integrity.\r\n\r\n2. Complete Alcohol Ban on the premises: Ensure clear-headed decision-making. This should include closure of all bars.",
